FBIS3-16759 "drsov054_b_94015" FBIS-SOV-94-054 Document Type:Daily Report 20 Mar 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Rutskoy Cited on Presidency LD2003162894 Moscow 2x2 Television in Russian 1230 GMT 20 Mar 94 LD2003162894 Moscow 2x2 Television Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Aleksandr Rutskoy might agree to be put forward as a candidate for the post of Russian president, if there is a clear and definite objective need for me as a leader. The former vice president said this in an interview to the Japanese KYODO agency, noting that he has sufficient knowledge and strength to conduct an election campaign and then head the state.
